
=========================
= 		INSTALL			=
=========================
   +
   |
   |
   +{1}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   Run a standard shell from GAIA source directory                                                                |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ cat script/sh/template/GAIA.bashrc >> ~/.bashrc && source ~/.bashrc             +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +{2}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   list all available LABSIM software ecosystem                                                                   |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-ecosystem --available                                                      +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |       Alternatively for a more complete description of each available LABSIM software ecosystem, run :           |
   |   |       +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+    |
   |   |       +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-ecosystem --available --detail | vi -                                      +    |
   |   |       +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+    |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +{3}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   then, simply deploy                                                                                            |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-deploy --ecosystem <your_ecosystem_version>                                +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +{4}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   finally, print installed config                                                                                |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-ecosystem                                                                  +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +